```

### Tipos de evento publicados

| Tipo | Origem | Payload principal |
|------|--------|-------------------|
| `message_received` | `router.py` â†’ `get_response(notify_received=True)` | `channel`, `user_id`, `message` |
| `intent_detected` | `graph.py` â†’ `identify_intent` | `user_id`, `channel`, `message`, `intent`, `confidence` |
| `response_sent` | `graph.py` â†’ `send_response` | `user_id`, `channel`, `message`, `response`, `intent` |
| `escalated` | `graph.py` â†’ `send_response` (quando `should_escalate=True`) | idem `response_sent` |

Formato JSON de cada evento:

```json
{
  "type": "intent_detected",
  "timestamp": "2026-05-30T12:00:00+00:00",
  "user_id": "...",
  "channel": "telegram",
  "message": "...",
  "intent": "question",
  "confidence": 0.92
}
```

